high_descs: Begin walking forward, then hang a right and walk over to the round white table in the corner of the room.
Pick up the large metal spoon white a black handle off of the round white table.
Turn left and begin walking across the room, then turn left again and walk over to the kitchen sink.
Wash the large metal spoon in the kitchen sink, then pick it back up.
Turn right and begin walking to the wall, then hang a right and walk over to the round white table in the corner of the room.
Place the clean large metal spoon on the table to the left of the loaves of bread.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean large metal spoon on the round white table.

high_descs: Turn right and walk across the room and take a right past the counter and walk forward and turn to face the kitchen table on the left.
Pick up the ladle on the far side of the kitchen table.
Turn left and walk forward and to the left to face the sink.
Wash the ladle in the sink, then pick it back up.
Turn around and walk forward and to the left to face the right side of the kitchen table.
Place the ladle back in the spot it was originally in.
anns.task_desc: To clean a ladle and put it back on the kitchen table.

high_descs: Turn right and walk across the kitchen until you get to the round table.
Grab the spoon to the left of the tomato.
Turn left, then turn right at the counter and walk until you reach the sink.
Wash the spoon in the sink.
Walk back to the round table.
Place the spoon to the left of the first loaf of bread on the table.
anns.task_desc: Place a washed spoon on a table.
